import React from 'react' const FlightInfo = ({info,loading}) => { const p = info; const hours = Math.floor(p[1] / 60); const minutes = 0; const duration = `${hours}h ${minutes === 0 ? null : minutes}min`; return loading ? ( null ) : (

Plane Number

{p[0]}

Duration

{duration}

Origin gate

{p[2]}

Destination gate

{p[3]}

) } export default FlightInfo
